<br>
The girl is somewhat paranoid, hoards food, and tries to avoid getting hit whenever possible. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://psiunit9.homestead.com/files/Imaru3a_copy.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=roninsenshi>RoninSenshi</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Senshi No Adakia<br>Jihad on that ass!</span><br>  Posts: 2086<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(7/14/03 5:36 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4591.topic&index=26>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/sageofthehalo/Shintou.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Sprit of Fighting.</span><hr size=1> For once I think I'd like a non insaneo character.<br>
